'''组蛋白脱乙酰酶类'''（{{lang-en|Histone deacetylases}}，{{EC number|3.5.1.98}}，简称为''HDAC''）是能将[[组蛋白|组蛋白]][[赖氨酸|赖氨酸]]上ε-''N''-[[乙酰基|乙酰基]]（O=C-CH<sub>3</sub>）水解掉的一类酶，这使得DNA缠绕组蛋白更加紧密。这点非常重要，因为[[DNA|DNA]]缠绕着组蛋白，而DNA的表达水平受到组蛋白乙酰化与脱乙酰化水平的影响。该酶的作用与{{le|组蛋白乙酰转移酶|Histone acetyltransferase|组蛋白乙酰转移酶（HAT）}}对冲。HDAC蛋白现在亦被称为赖氨酸脱乙酰酶类（KDAC），这样做的目的是为了突出其功能而非其靶点，因其作用靶点亦包括了非组蛋白的蛋白质类<ref name="pmid19608861">{{cite journal | author = Choudhary C | title = Lysine acetylation targets protein complexes and co-regulates major cellular functions | journal = Science | volume = 325 | issue = 5942 | pages = 834–40 | pmid = 19608861 | doi = 10.1126/science.1175371 | url = http://www.sciencemag.org/cgi/content/full/325/5942/834 | issn = 1095-9203 | author-separator = , | display-authors = 1 | last2 = Kumar | first2 = C. | last3 = Gnad | first3 = F. | last4 = Nielsen | first4 = M. L. | last5 = Rehman | first5 = M. | last6 = Walther | first6 = T. C. | last7 = Olsen | first7 = J. V. | last8 = Mann | first8 = M. |date=August 2009}}</ref>。

